@startuml 龍蝦技術中心 - 簡化版
!theme cerulean-outline
skinparam ParticipantPadding 25
skinparam SequenceMessagePadding 15
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

title 龍蝦技術中心 - Sub-session 協作模式

actor "User" as User
participant "主代理\n(Tech Expert)" as Main
box "龍蝦工程師團隊 (Sub-sessions)" #FFF3E0
    participant "架構 / 開發 / 測試\n(Sub-agents)" as Lobsters
end box

User -> Main: 提出需求
activate Main

Main -> Lobsters: sessions_spawn()
note right: 並行派生多個子會議\n各專注單一職責
activate Lobsters

Lobsters -> Lobsters: 並行執行任務
Lobsters -> Main: 回傳結果
deactivate Lobsters

Main -> Main: 整合成果
Main -> User: 交付解決方案
deactivate Main

note over Main, Lobsters
Sub-session 架構: 主代理派生獨立子會議
核心設計: 單一職責 + 並行執行 + 統籌交付
技術機制: sessions_spawn (創建) | sessions_send (溝通)
end note

@enduml
